Plot counties

p <- ggplot(cnty, aes(long, lat, group = group)) + 
  geom_polygon(aes(fill = region), 
               show.legend = FALSE, 
               colour = rgb(1, 1, 1, 0.2)) + 
  coord_quickmap()+
  theme_void()
